'''''Akounak Tedalat Taha Tazoughai''''', ni filime yumuziki yo muri [[Nigeriya]] ya 2015 iyobowe na Christopher Kirkley  yakozwe na Sahel Sounds<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/event/films-on-the-green-akounak-tedalat-taha-tazoughai/</ref>, L'Improbable na Tenere Films.   Niyo filime yambere yisi ya Tuareg -ururimi rwimpimbano<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4675526/</ref>.  Filime ishingiye kubintu byabayeho mubuzima bwa Mdou Moctar <ref>https://frenchculture.org/events/13394-virtual-cinemaakounak-tedalat-taha-tazoughai</ref>. 

Filime yafatiwe ahitwa Agadez, muri [[Nijeriya]].<ref>https://www.theatlantic.com/international/archive/2015/02/purple-rain-in-the-saharan-desert/385234/</ref> Filime yakiriwe neza kandi yegukana ibihembo byinshi mubirori mpuzamahanga bya firime<ref>https://www.soundohm.com/product/akounak-tedalat-taha-tazo</ref>.   Nibyunvikiro byikinamico ya Prince yo mu ''1984 Imvura yumutuku''<ref>https://www.imdb.com/title/tt4675526/</ref> .

